Package: StatModels
Title: Interactive Statistical Modeling Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for statistical modeling,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for linear models (LM),
    generalized linear models (GLM), generalized additive models (GAM), and
    linear mixed models (LMM/GLMM). Designed for teaching and research in
    ecology and biodiversity sciences.
